          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0362P0_20010131_WH_16'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-julia-drown' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0362P0_20010131_WH_16' title='Link to this speech by Ms Julia Drown' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
